# Macros:
#   P:        The PV name as BLEN:(AREA):(POS)
#   P0/1:     The PV name as BLEN:(AREA):(POS):(INST)A/B
#   SCAN:     Scan rate for PVs. Should keep below 1Hz, 2Hz max rate
